{
  "stem": "23090.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We went up on a ramp like a-- it was like a wooden plank with some blocks underneath.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, because these cattle wagons were high, and the ground was obviously low.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there were no ladders or anything like that, so they put these wooden planks and they started herding us into these wagons.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And all you kept hearing is schnell, fast, schnell, schnell.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You there, schnell, this, this, this, and this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I can tell you that-- that the things that we did have to take, we couldn't get in, because we dropped it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the only thing you wound up, maybe, was with some pillow or some pair of shoes or something and the-- and the clothes you wore.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] they loaded us up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "If this cattle car held 80 people, there must have been 150 people because I could not breathe.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "My dad had to restrain people, you know, so we could breathe.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the screaming and hollering and the-- that's Dante's inferno began.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The beginning of the end just began right there for me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The nightmare was--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother and-- well, our neighbors.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some of the neighbors, some people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, the ghetto was basically a small place and--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You don't know everybody, but it's something that-- but that all goes out the window.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Friends?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It just goes out the window.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The ba-- the-- the-- this-- the beginning of survival becomes the focus point.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And unfortunately, I have to tell you that it takes precedence over everything else, the survival.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
